# â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•â•

prod: ## Build production-optimized version
	$(MAKE) build-optimized
	@echo "$(GREEN)âœ“ Production build completed$(NC)"

release-package: clean prod docs ## Create release package
	@echo "$(BLUE)Creating release package...$(NC)"
	@mkdir -p dist
	@tar -czf dist/vimmacs-$$(cargo metadata --no-deps --format-version 1 | jq -r '.packages[0].version')-$(PLATFORM).tar.gz \
		-C $(RELEASE_DIR) vimmacs \
		-C $(PROJECT_ROOT) README.md LICENSE* \
